channel.title: Looking for Developers for my new project!
channel.description:
[center][center][center][img]http://i554.photobucket.com/albums/jj409/xxxglitcherxxx/444483_orig.png[/img][/center]
I'm looking for 1 or 2 to help develop my new runescape private server. This server is a re-vamped version of Acheron which you can google and find v1-v4 and find out what I'm talking about. Please if you interested Please! Message me or facebook me below which is the fastest way you can reach me.*add me on facebook so i can receive your message!* *You must have experience with coding and i need proof of your experience!* [img]http://i554.photobucket.com/albums/jj409/xxxglitcherxxx/f.png[/img][/center]
[center]Ill add update logs as the days pass[/center]
